<doc id="1254405" wikidata="Q4630963" url="?curid=1254405" title="219 Days">
<text>219 Days is the debut album of &quot;Canadian Idol&quot; winner Kalan Porter. The album was released on November 23, 2004 through Sony Music Canada. The album title refers to the number of days from his first audition to the release of his debut CD. The album debuted at #4 on the Canadian Albums Chart and was certified double platinum by the CRIA months later with an excess of 200,000 copies.

