Replacing formula_17 by formula_18 gives
{2!}f&quot;(x) + \frac{8h^{3}}{3!}f&quot;&#x27;(x) + ...&lt;/math&gt;|}}

Multiplying identity () by 4 gives
{2!}f&quot;(x) + \frac{4h^{3}}{3!}f&quot;&#x27;(x) + ...&lt;/math&gt;|}}

